    .get-started.row-grey.show-for-large-up
        .row
            .large-12.columns
                ul.large-block-grid-2
                    li
                        h2 Get started in just 2 steps
                        .row.step-1.step(rel="line-1")
                            .small-2.columns 1
                            .small-10.columns
                                h4 Include Handsontable CSS and JavaScript files
                                p
                                    | Make sure you're adding them properly. #{''}
                                    a(href="https://github.com/handsontable/handsontable/releases/tag/0.15.0-beta3", target="_blank") Download the latest release #{""}
